OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early brightness in
OL,6,Fsoutheast, but generally a cloudy
OL,7,Fmorning with outbreaks of occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy rain. During the afternoon the
OL,9,Frain turns more showery and perhaps
OL,10,Fthundery.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowery rain will push
OL,13,Fnortheast through the evening,
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy and perhaps
OL,15,Fthundery at times. Clear spells and
OL,16,Fscattered showers overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,19,Fshowers in the morning, turning drier
OL,20,Fin the afternoon. Cloudier with some
OL,21,Frain in the late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
